&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ripple’s Creator Fund was developed to foster innovation in tokenization, with a focus on non-fungible tokens (NFTs). The fund provides targeted support for creators, brands and marketplaces to explore new use cases for NFTs on the XRP Ledger (XRPL), leveraging its innate advantages of speed, cost and sustainability.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ripple is looking to hire a Program Manager for the Creator Fund program. As a member of the RippleX team, you will engage with external developers, agencies, creators, and brands to bring a diverse set of tokenization projects to the XRP Ledger. You will own the $250M Creator Fund, leading strategy and operational execution of the fund, and ensure all participants have an excellent experience from their application to execution of NFT projects.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Build and own the operating model for administering $250M to NFT ecosystem participants building on XRPL.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Handle pre- and post-fund administration and oversight of projects.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Manage strategy and day to day execution with marketplaces, agencies, creators, and brands.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Own the budget, planning, and allocation of resources across projects.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Develop streamlined approval processes with relevant internal stakeholders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Drive and ensure regular, ongoing communication and coordination across functions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Facilitate efficient meetings to ensure information exchange and alignment across teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Monitor, analyze, and report on the fund applicants and their progress over time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Define and measure success metrics, and assist with the preparation of progress reports.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work collaboratively with Legal and Finance to create effective and efficient disbursement processes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Recommend and contribute to process improvements, including product enhancements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coordinate with Marketing to promote and drive applicants to ensure the ongoing success of the Creator Fund.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
