&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Be responsible for creating sales opportunities for Commodities Settlement and Optimization products in a network growth environment. Success is being able to convince banks and brokers to work with Paxos and to advance their settlement processes to Simultaneous settlement through our regulated Trust Company. Developing relationships and managing stakeholders to close deals, as well as being able to analyse the ROI we can offer our clients, is critical.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
